name: Evolve Cyber Security Index Fund
longDescription: The Evolve Cyber Security Index Fund (the Fund) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Global Cyber Security Index (the Benchmark), or any successor thereto. The Fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies located domestically or internationally that are involved in the cyber security industry through hardware and software development.
